values:
we did an exercise in drivers ed were we put on these "drunk" goggles  
it was disgusting  
the second i put them on i felt sick 

i miss my sister more than ever 
         no exaggeration. 
i dont know what is going on with dreamy boy 
i have a vocab test tomorrow and spelling too 
       i hate vocab and spelling 
i miss my home 
i miss my egg roll 
i miss sharing memories 
i miss victoria 
i want to be shorter than my sister again 
i want to make brownies with her  
i want to want to forget everything and be free from it all 

i get it and dont need to be told again

ok
so i went to visit y'all
i posted telling ya to call me if you wanted to see me
ONLY 4 PEOPLE CAME!!
oh well.
i had a blast!
we hung out at the mall and had fun then i went to KKs home
I ATE 5 PEICES OF PIZZA!!!!
it was really good though!
lol!
so, the next day i went to khols to look for jeans
I DIDNT FIND ANY THAT FIT!
typical pant experience
so i went again to other stores the next day
I STILL DIDNT FIND ANY!!!
curses to my giant butt!

i got my kitten on tuesday
i dont know if i told y'all that yet
she is soooo cute!
she is orange with golden honey eyes!
she is absolutely perfect!
she likes to snuggle
she likes to play 
AND
she purrs soooo loud!
hehe!
I love her so much!

the stupid person who was supposed to appraize our house did it wrong the first time
then he went on vacation 
so
we were supposed to get it on the 14th
NOW
we cant move in till like the 28th
grrrrr!
i have no home!
stupid appraizal man!

guys!!!
i cant figure out how to put a background on my profile page
it looks so......
white!

OMG!!!! this is crap!!
i just spent like 30 minutes typing this and it disappeared!
AAAAA!
i want to squish a bug!!
MGRRRRR!
well, ill give you the shortened version
i left on friday for my dad's rental house 
there is NOTHING to do here!!
so
we went to walmart (basiclly the only store here)
where some stupid lady cut me in line in the walmart restrooms
I HAD TO PEE!!!
and she CUT me!
what is that!?
afterwards we went on a walk in the woods
there are alot of those here
i got to see an arrastra
ya
thats what the people used in the old days to  grind up gold ore
it is basically a long log attatched to two bolders that a donkey pulls in a circle
..........
so anyways
then i went to see my grandpa
that was nice
he has the GREATEST stories
he was in the marines
he is a real live miner with a pick and ax
and he has been through the craziest situations!!
   can ya tell i think he is the greatest?lol
while i was there i got to see my kitten!
she is already getting bigger!
i cant wait till we get our house so i can keep her with me!

i spent last night watching the halmark channel
i stayed up until 2 oclock watching stranded and Marco Polo
i woke up this moring at 1:45
or is that this afternoon?
hehe!

im feeling kinda lonely
i miss my person
I LOVE YOU!!!!!
